<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM6.5.6">
<l>pakuvāy vaṉpēy koṅkai cuvaittā ruyiruṇṭu</l>
<l>pukuvāy niṉṟa pōta kamvīḻap porutāṉūr</l>
<l>nekuvāy neytal pūma tumāntik kamalattiṉ</l>
<l>nakuvāy malarmē laṉṉa muṟaṅkum naṟaiyūrē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The city of the one who fought so that the elephant,</l>
<l rend="indent">which stood in the entrance, fell,</l>
<l>Having [once] tasted the breast of the strong demoness with a gaping mouth,</l>
<l rend="indent">consuming her dear life,</l>
<l>Is Naṟaiyūr where swans doze on lotus blossoms with smiling lips,</l>
<l>Having sipped nectar from waterlily flowers with soft lips.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
